# Hub Gateway image (Dockerfile.hub) build context. node_modules is reinstalled
# inside the image by `bun install`, and the proxy runs from source (src/), so
# none of these are needed in the COPY — excluding them cuts the build context
# from ~600MB to a few MB and speeds the VPS build.
node_modules
dist
.git
*.log
*.tsbuildinfo
.DS_Store
# SECURITY: never bake local secrets into the image. .env.providers / .env.local
# hold real provider keys and are NOT needed at runtime (the container gets its
# env from compose's env_file). Matches src/web/.dockerignore.
.env*
*.pem
.credentials.json
